# iOS — CocoaPods downloads (Podfile.lock is enough to reproduce them)
**/ios/Pods/
**/ios/.symlinks/

# iOS — auto-generated by flutter pub get / flutter build
**/ios/Flutter/Generated.xcconfig
**/ios/Flutter/flutter_export_environment.sh
**/ios/Flutter/App.framework
**/ios/Flutter/Flutter.framework
**/ios/Flutter/Flutter.podspec

# iOS — per-developer Xcode state (breakpoints, window layout, open tabs)
**/ios/xcuserdata/
**/*.xcuserstate

### Xcode ###
## User settings
xcuserdata/

